==============================================================================
Open standards
==============================================================================

PromptWise emits and interoperates with the following open standards. These are
protocols/conventions, not bundled third-party software — PromptWise ships no
external framework code and runs entirely on its own engine.

- Model Context Protocol (MCP) — open standard — https://modelcontextprotocol.io
- AGENTS.md                    — open convention — https://agents.md
- SKILL.md                     — portable skill format (YAML frontmatter + prompt)

==============================================================================
Third-party Python dependencies
==============================================================================

Standard PyPI packages declared in pyproject.toml (mcp, tiktoken, pydantic,
pyyaml, aiosqlite, aiohttp, flask, SQLAlchemy, jsonschema, prometheus-client,
Authlib, anthropic) are used under their respective licenses.
